en_274025_0	A donation programme was organized for the people living in rural areas of Kilinochchi by Army personnel under the supervision of the Commander, Security Forces - Kilinochchi (SF-KLN), Major General Vijitha Ravipriya and following coordination done by the 57 Division Headquarters of the Security Force Headquarters - Kilinochchi, (SFHQ-KLN) on Friday (28).
en_274025_1	Thanks to the sponsorship provided by the ‘Daham Pahana’ Organization at the request of the SFHQ-KLN, 20 families received solar panels and 100 pupils were awarded sport items and school accessories under the project.
en_274025_2	Catholic priests, General Officer Commanding, 57 Division, Brigade Commanders, Senior Officers, Officers and Other Ranks and civilians participated in the event.
